sentences.english: Jingming acupoint is located in the pit above slightly the inner canthus.
sentences.chinese: 睛明穴位於眼睛內眼角稍上方凹陷處。

sentences.english: Slightly press below the eye from inner corner of eye to outer corner of eye with ring finger.
sentences.chinese: 用無名指在眼睛下方由內眼角向外眼角輕按。

sentences.english: FENG CHI(GB20) is effective as well to the sufferer of hypertension with inner eye corner pain.
sentences.chinese: 高血壓病人常會出現兩側內眼角的脹痛，用之亦效。
